sem_rt$pathlengthfac = ordered(as.factor(as.character(sem_rt$pathlength)), 
                            levels = c("1", "2", "3", "4", "6", "15"))
sem_rt$subject = as.factor(sem_rt$subject)
rt_aov = aov(data = sem_rt, rt ~ pathlengthfac + 
                     Error(subject/(pathlengthfac)))
